                            </p>
                            <p id="p-1302" data-page="33480">8. Section 435.907 is amended by&mdash;</p>
                            <p id="p-1303" data-page="33480">a. Removing paragraph (c)(4); and</p>
                            <p id="p-1304" data-page="33480">b. Revising paragraph (d).</p>
                            <p id="p-1305" data-page="33480">The revision reads as follows:</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="section">
                            <div class="sectno sectno-reference" id="sectno-reference-435.907"><a href="#sectno-citation-435.907">&sect;&thinsp;435.907</a></div>
