</div>
                            <p id="p-1307" data-page="33480">(c) For each individual who has submitted an application described in &sect;&thinsp;435.907 or whose eligibility is being renewed in accordance with &sect;&thinsp;435.916 and who meets the non-financial requirements for eligibility (or for whom the agency is providing a reasonable opportunity to verify citizenship or immigration status in accordance with &sect;&thinsp;435.956(b)), the State Medicaid agency must comply with the following&mdash;</p>
