                            <span class="auth-header">Authority: </span>
                            <span class="auth-content"><a href="https://www.govinfo.gov/link/uscode/42/1302" class="usc external" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">42 U.S.C. 1302</a>. </span>
