<span class="icon-fr2 icon-fr2-star">* </span><span class="icon-fr2 icon-fr2-star">* </span><span class="icon-fr2 icon-fr2-star">* </span><span class="icon-fr2 icon-fr2-star">* </span><span class="icon-fr2 icon-fr2-star">*</span>
</div>
